The '''Association for Tourism in Higher Education''' (ATHE), is a [[learned society]] in the [[United Kingdom]] dedicated to promoting tourism as a subject of study in the UK. It encourages high standards in learning, teaching and research. It is a member of the [[Academy of Social Sciences]].<ref>http://acss.org.uk/mem-soc/</ref>
